{"id":300434,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/06/global-voices-巴西：免费宣传海报声援车票上涨抗争/","date":"2013-06-23T11:16:07Z","modified":"2013-06-23T11:16:07Z","title":"Global Voices | 巴西：免费宣传海报声援车票上涨抗争","content":"<p><div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=607797899244577&#038;set=a.498803880143980.115805.491087744248927&#038;type=1\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-43930\" alt=\"Gráfica imprime gratuitamente cartazes com ideias de manifestantes em São Paulo. Foto por Meli-Melo Press, publicada no Facebook.\" src=\"http://pt.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/1009371_607797899244577_1087523004_o-375x255.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"255\" /></a></p>\n<p>巴西圣保罗的出版商公开征件，免费替抗议公车票调涨的示威群众输出海报。照片来自Meli-Melo的脸书。</p>\n</div>\n<p>出版与设计工作室<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/MeliMeloPress\">Meli-Melo</a>，决定支援圣保罗<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/06/14/brazil-protesters-take-to-the-streets-of-sao-paulo-against-increased-bus-fare/\">抗议公车票调涨的抗争活动</a>，提供设备免费输出海报。<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=607679765923057&#038;set=a.498803880143980.115805.491087744248927&#038;type=1\">6月14日星期五，工作室在脸书上公开征求海报设计</a>葡，许多抗议群众迅速回覆。几小时之后，好几份海报皆已印制完成，准备好进行定于6月17日星期一举行的抗争活动。</p>\n<div>校对者：Rio</div>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://pt.globalvoicesonline.org/author/joaomiguel/\" title=\"文章导读 João Miguel D. de A. Lima\">João Miguel D. de A. Lima</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/ameli/\" title=\"文章导读 Ameli\">Ameli</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://pt.globalvoicesonline.org/2013/06/15/brasil-grafica-cartazes-protestos-sao-paulo/\" title=\"阅读原文  pt\">阅读原文  pt</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.o